title: The Brass Pickle
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A deli with vegetarian sandwiches, of which some may be vegan or can be made vegan; please inquire. Also has a wide assortment of vegetables to custom create your own sandwiches including alfalfa sprouts, avocados, tomatoes, mushrooms, peppercinis and more. Serves some gluten free items.
